@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam wrapWidth 180
skinparam maxMessageSize 90
skinparam ArrowColor #6B6B6B
skinparam ArrowFontColor #666666
skinparam ArrowFontStyle bold
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 0
  BorderThickness 1
}
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #555555
  BorderStyle dashed
  BackgroundColor transparent
  FontColor #444444
  FontStyle bold
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #C9332B
  BorderColor #C9332B
  FontColor #FFFFFF
}
hide stereotype
title ElectroCorp - Backend General Components Diagram
left to right direction


rectangle "<b>ElectroCorp Web App</b>
<size:12><i>[External Container]</i></size>

Angular SPA consuming backend services." as WebApp <#7F8C8D>
package "ElectroCorp Backend API / Spring Boot
[container]" {
  rectangle "<b>REST API Entry Point</b>
<size:12><i>[Spring Boot Application]</i></size>

Receives HTTP requests and delegates to bounded contexts." as Api <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Shared Kernel API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Health Controller, Global Exception Handler, Security Filter Chain." as B0 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>IAM API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Auth Controller, User Controller, Authentication Application Service." as B1 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Billing API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Billing Controller, Plan Application Service, Subscription Application Service." as B2 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Workplace API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Workplace Controller, Location Application Service, Room Application Service." as B3 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Device Control API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Device Control Controller, Device Application Service, Device Group Application Service." as B4 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Energy Monitoring API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Energy Monitoring Controller, Reading Application Service, Dashboard Query Service." as B5 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Notifications API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Notifications Controller, Alert Application Service, Alert Rule Application Service." as B6 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Reporting API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Reporting Controller, Platform Insight Controller, Report Application Service." as B7 <#3498DB>
  rectangle "<b>Service Management API</b>
<size:12><i>[Bounded Context Component]</i></size>

Service Management Controller, Support Ticket Application Service, Maintenance Ticket Application Service." as B8 <#3498DB>
}
database "<b>ElectroCorp Database</b>
<size:12><i>[Relational Database]</i></size>

Stores backend data for every bounded context." as Database
WebApp --> Api : Consumes REST endpoints (JSON / HTTPS)
Api --> B0 : Routes request
Api --> B1 : Routes request
Api --> B2 : Routes request
Api --> B3 : Routes request
